### No tool call
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{OPEN_AI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4.1-mini",
  "input": "I am traveling to Boulder, CO tomorrow. What clothing should I pack?",
